{
  "stem": "25027.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, on January 8th or 10th or 11th, I'm not sure which exact date, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they dismantled all the-- the mortars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hooked up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were on the move again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We heard firing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Artillery opened up early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The sky lit up at 4:00 in the morning like it was daylight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Russian planes were bombing the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were softening them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Katushas-- I don't know if you know what katushas are-- were firing by the thousands, these rockets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we waited from about 4:00 or 5:00 in the morning till 7:00.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were on the move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Apparently the infantry broke through to the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Wisla River was frozen solid, like a rock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The trucks went right across.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we came into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Warsaw, there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was rubble, the whole city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't see-- as we were driving through Warsaw, I didn't see one standing building that wasn't damaged or destroyed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we didn't stay in Warsaw, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We drove right through it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we kept advancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we came to where the Germans tried to hold on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We opened fire for a few hours, and we moved on again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They-- we broke through again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And each week, we broke through again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And each two weeks, we broke through again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we got to-- to this place where we found-- where-- were I found these Hungarian women in a-- in this Hungarian camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see much of the camp, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We drove in, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I see the ditch beside the road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we see bodies moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
